(NCDOT Counts 13-07169 thru 13-07175 were counted on a rotating schedule)
Data Collection Method: Jamar Count Boards (Unit #s TU-1226 & TU-1227))
1) Gregory Math, Science, & Technology Elementary, Williston
Middle, & New Hanover High Schools are located less than 1
mile from the studied intersection, however were not in
session on the date of the count - as all New Hanover County
Schools were still out of session for summer break.
2) Of the pedestrians observed & counted, one wheelchair bound
ped crossed the SB leg of South 17
4) Area lighting was present at the count location.
5) No highway construction was observed that impacted normal
6) Data collection equipment was operating correctly at time of count.
7) Counters took a break from 2:00 – 2:30 PM. Data for this period was interpolated.
8) The counters did not have any additional notes.
